00:21:51.101 --> 00:21:52.728
[ Panting ]

517
00:21:52.812 --> 00:21:55.105
No. no! Let me go! No!

518
00:21:55.189 --> 00:21:56.565
Boom. Egged!

519
00:21:56.649 --> 00:21:57.858
It's okay.

520
00:21:57.900 --> 00:21:59.819
He's an alien
who removes his intelligence

521
00:21:59.860 --> 00:22:01.070
to hook up with locals.

522
00:22:01.153 --> 00:22:02.363
He likes that you're simple.

523
00:22:02.446 --> 00:22:04.240
He doesn't want to be known.

524
00:22:05.407 --> 00:22:07.243
Did you get any of that?
